---
title: Cal Smart Chipotle-Honey Beyond Meat® Bowls with Green Onion Rice
description: This hearty Beyond Meat® bowl is full of wholesome goodness! We even snuck some spinach into the Beyond Meat® mix for an added veggie boost. Pickled radishes and a sweet and spicy chipotle-honey sauce brighten each bite.

